  "description": "A nighttime view of a marina filled with various boats. The water is dark and reflective, mirroring the lights from the boats and a few distant structures. Several sailboats with tall masts dominate the scene, their silhouettes against the dark sky. A small, red rowboat is visible in the foreground near a sandy shoreline. The boats range in size and color, with some appearing white and others darker. The overall scene conveys a sense of tranquility and peacefulness, with a subtle starry sky above.",
